unlocked_quests.title: Level 30 Character (FINAL FANTASY X)
unlocked_quests.description:
Raise a character from FINAL FANTASY X to level 30!
When fighting in dungeons from their native realm, characters get a Record Synergy bonus.
The Record Synergy bonus boosts characters' stats and the EXP they earn.
Recruit characters from each realm to have the perfect party ready at a moment's notice!
unlocked_quests.achieve_cond_description: Raise any character from the FINAL FANTASY X realm to level 30 or higher.

quest.title: Level 10 Character (FINAL FANTASY X)
quest.description:
Raise a character from FINAL FANTASY X to level 10!
Wakka is a character from the FINAL FANTASY X realm who can be recruited by completing the Besaid (X) dungeon .
When fighting in dungeons from their native realm, characters get a Record Synergy bonus.
The Record Synergy bonus boosts characters' stats and the EXP they earn.
Recruit characters from each realm to have the perfect party ready at a moment's notice!
quest.achieve_cond_description: Raise any character from the FINAL FANTASY X realm to level 10 or higher.
